            <ie/>, one newton<ndash/>meter,
            or <quantity>
                <unit prefix="kilo" base="gram"/><unit base="meter"/><per base="second" exp="2"/>
               </quantity><quantity><unit base="meter"/></quantity>
            In Imperial Units, it is ft<ndash/>lb.
